provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/multiprocessing.html — Python multiprocessing documentation"
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/multiprocessing.shared_memory.html — Python shared memory documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/multiprocessing/pool.py, Lib/multiprocessing/process.py, Lib/multiprocessing/queues.py, Lib/multiprocessing/synchronize.py, Lib/multiprocessing/shared_memory.py, Lib/multiprocessing/managers.py, Lib/multiprocessing/connection.py"
  notes:
    - "This spec covers: multiprocessing.pool.Pool — __doc__.__len__()==75; __name__=='Pool' (len=4); __module__=='multiprocessing.pool' (len=20). multiprocessing.process.BaseProcess — __doc__.__len__()==116; __name__=='BaseProcess' (len=11); __module__=='multiprocessing.process' (len=23). multiprocessing.queues.Queue — __name__=='Queue' (len=5); __module__=='multiprocessing.queues' (len=22); no __doc__. multiprocessing.queues.JoinableQueue — __name__=='JoinableQueue' (len=13); __module__=='multiprocessing.queues' (len=22). multiprocessing.queues.SimpleQueue — __name__=='SimpleQueue' (len=11); __module__=='multiprocessing.queues' (len=22). multiprocessing.synchronize.Semaphore — __name__=='Semaphore' (len=9); __module__=='multiprocessing.synchronize' (len=27). multiprocessing.synchronize.Lock — __name__=='Lock' (len=4); __module__=='multiprocessing.synchronize' (len=27). multiprocessing.shared_memory.SharedMemory — __doc__.__len__()==709; __name__=='SharedMemory' (len=12); __module__=='multiprocessing.shared_memory' (len=29). multiprocessing.managers.BaseManager — __doc__.__len__()==25; __name__=='BaseManager' (len=11); __module__=='multiprocessing.managers' (len=24). multiprocessing.connection.Connection — __doc__.__len__()==99; __name__=='Connection' (len=10); __module__=='multiprocessing.connection' (len=26). All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "multiprocessing.pool.Pool.__module__=='multiprocessing.pool' (len=20); multiprocessing.process.BaseProcess.__module__=='multiprocessing.process' (len=23); multiprocessing.queues subclasses all share __module__=='multiprocessing.queues' (len=22); multiprocessing.synchronize subclasses all share __module__=='multiprocessing.synchronize' (len=27, the longest synchronize module name in this spec); multiprocessing.shared_memory.SharedMemory.__module__=='multiprocessing.shared_memory' (len=29, the longest module name in this spec); multiprocessing.managers.BaseManager.__module__=='multiprocessing.managers' (len=24); multiprocessing.connection.Connection.__module__=='multiprocessing.connection' (len=26). All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

